definition: to exist/to deposit/to store/to keep/to survive

sentences.english: They could soon take it to the next level by excising the traditional navigation toolbar.
sentences.chinese: 下一步他们很快就会把手伸向现存的传统导航工具栏。

sentences.english: Existing mathematic theory couldn’t explain it.
sentences.chinese: 现存的数学理论无法解释它。

sentences.english: The Codex Sinaiticus is the world's oldest surviving bible.
sentences.chinese: 西奈抄本是世界上现存最古老的圣经。

sentences.english: The closest living analogue might be a sponge.
sentences.chinese: 现存的最接近的类似物或许是海绵。

sentences.english: The existing time-stamp protocols were introduced and their shortcomings were analysed when used in an unsafe domain and proposed hierarchical time-stamp protocol (HTSP).
sentences.chinese: 分析了目前现存的几个时间戳协议以及各自的优缺点。

sentences.english: It is the extant and earliest monograph on dietetic treatment.
sentences.chinese: 这是现存最早的专着和饮食治疗。

sentences.english: Sutra of the Ten Kings, now in British Museum.
sentences.chinese: 地藏十王图画圈，现存大英博物馆。

sentences.english: The existing industrial building has a cast iron column structure.
sentences.chinese: 这栋现存的工业建筑结构为铁柱结构。

sentences.english: The Poems for Imperial Reading is a rarely extant collection of the Tang writings.
sentences.chinese: 《御览诗》为现存少数唐人选集的一种。

sentences.english: 《The Xiaozheng Chinese Calandar》(XCC) is one of China's extant and oldest scientific documents.
sentences.chinese: 《夏小正》是我国现存最古老的科学文献之一。

sentences.english: The toolbar also supplies an icon to re-run the existing report.
sentences.chinese: 工具栏也提供了一个图标来重新运行现存的报表。

sentences.english: Aisin Gioro descendents now are from other branches of the family.
sentences.chinese: 爱新觉罗家现存后裔都是旁支。

sentences.english: Tianyi Pavilion Library is the earliest library of China.
sentences.chinese: 天一阁是我国目前现存的最早的私人藏书楼。

sentences.english: Nowdays, there are only six existing boiling wells , well water half clear half muddy.
sentences.chinese: 现存古沸井有六口，井水三清三浊。

sentences.english: Three of Archimedes' extant works are devoted to plane geometry.
sentences.chinese: 阿基米德现存的三部著作都是献给平面几何的。

sentences.english: Although 1,000 were printed, very few are known to remain in existence.
sentences.chinese: 虽然有印了1000张，但已知的现存卡非常少。
